snippet.title: Diehard Dungeon v1.4 Trailer
snippet.description:
Please vote for Diehard Dungeon on Steam Greenlight: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=93316971

Diehard Dungeon is a real-time roguelike dungeon crawler.

Visit www.dieharddungeon.wordpress.com and follow @tricktale for game information and updates.

Diehard Dungeon is available to purchase from Desura and GamersGate.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
